sequenceDiagram
  participant U as User
  participant M as Model
  participant R as Runtime
  participant P as Permission
  participant L as Local Tools
  participant S as State/Audit

  U->>M: 修复测试失败
  M->>R: Glob intent
  R->>P: read/search policy
  P-->>R: allow
  R->>L: execute Glob
  L-->>R: candidate files
  R->>S: audit search
  R-->>M: observation

  M->>R: Read intent
  R->>P: read path policy
  P-->>R: allow
  R->>L: execute Read
  L-->>R: content + mtime
  R->>S: readFileState
  R-->>M: observation

  M->>R: Bash test intent
  R->>P: command policy
  P-->>R: ask/allow
  R->>L: execute Bash
  L-->>R: exitCode + output preview
  R->>S: audit command
  R-->>M: observation

  M->>R: Edit intent
  R->>S: verify read baseline
  R->>P: write policy
  P-->>R: ask/allow
  R->>L: apply edit
  L-->>R: diff
  R->>S: audit diff
  R-->>M: observation
